# Editorial style

Full detail: `.playbook/05_STYLE_GUIDE.md`.

- Professional, actionable, concise. Active voice; lead with the point. Mark fact vs inference explicitly.
- Sentence-case headings. Numbered = sequences; bullets = unordered; tables if >3 comparable attrs.
- Reuse terminology from `05_STYLE_GUIDE.md` (e.g. “Adobe Experience Manager (AEM)”). Don’t pad without density.
